            <div class="x6 last">
                <div>
                    <p>Residents of Scenic Acres have access to various basic amenities like parks, playgrounds, schools, libraries, shopping, theatres, recreational facilities, eateries, etc. Long-time residents of the neighbourhood enjoy a rewarding and peaceful life. Scenic Acres residences range from moderate to high-end homes. In this upscale community, there are also some villa units and attached townhouses.</p>
                    <p>The neighbourhood is located close to the huge Crowfoot Shopping Center, the University of Calgary, and the Foothills Hospital. That means residents have access to medical attention, education, and other amenities. The community features a pathway system, a few sports fields, tennis courts, an indoor skating rink, and a hockey rink.</p>
                    <p>The recent development of the Crowfoot LRT extension has given walkable access to the LTR station.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Shopping &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>The residents of Scenic Acres have access to more than 300 shops and services at nearby Crowfoot Crossing. These include dining, shopping, and entertainment options. Crowfoot Crossing is one of the best shopping places around. Crowfoot Crossing Shopping Center houses a Community Natural Foods grocery store and Lowes nearby. Access to downtown is easy via the Crowfoot LRT station.</p>
                    <p>The well-established Silver Springs community reachable by the Crowchild Trail is another neighbourhood that's good for shopping. If you don't mind travelling a little further down Crowchild Trail, the CF Mall at Varsity has a great selection of stores. It is an excellent combination of a shopping zone as well as entertainment. A free-play place at the centre of the mall is a safe area to keep your kids engaged while you shop.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Parks &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>Parks add recreational spaces to communities and are perks to a good residential neighbourhood. Fortunately, residents of Scenic Acres have plenty of choices when it comes to parks and playgrounds. They have access to the Scenic Acres Park, offering facilities like tennis courts, basketball courts, sports fields, a playground, and a trail.</p>
                    <p>Scurfield Park and Scenic Cove Park are located close to each other and are accessible easily by the residents of Scenic Acres. Scurfield Park has a playground, four sports fields, ball diamonds, and a multi-use pad.</p>
                    <p>Children living in the community can enjoy outdoor games at Sceptre playground and the Scenic Glen playground.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
