            <p>The northwest community was established decades back in 1981. Since the community's inception, it has made great progress in providing residents with everything that they need, including schools, medical facilities, transportation, eateries, public parks, etc. Being developed over the years, the neighbourhood provides an ideal mix of value, amenities, and conveniences required for cozy and secure living. </p>
